### Project: tint — All 5 phases (Tasks #757-761)
Zero-dependency Go terminal color library replacing fatih/color (26,630 importers, archived). Core Color type with 42 ANSI attributes, Sprint/Sprintf/Sprintln/Print/Printf/Println/Fprint/Fprintf/Fprintln, SprintFunc/SprintfFunc/SprintlnFunc/PrintFunc/PrintfFunc/PrintlnFunc/FprintFunc/FprintfFunc/FprintlnFunc, Set/Unset, DisableColor/EnableColor. Built-in isatty (Unix raw syscall TIOCGWINSZ, Windows GetConsoleMode, Plan9 /dev/cons). Windows colorable writer (ANSI-to-ConsoleAPI with VT passthrough). 256-color (Fg256/Bg256), 24-bit RGB (FgRGB/BgRGB), HiColor mixer. 16+16 convenience print/string functions. Global NoColor (NO_COLOR env, TERM=dumb), Output/Error writers. compat/color drop-in fatih/color replacement (type aliases). 91.7% coverage. 8 benchmarks. Go 1.21+, zero deps. CI green on ubuntu/macos/windows x Go 1.21/1.22/1.23.

